OL,3,CExpectant mum 'cried' when she found
OL,4,Cout maternity unit was closing
OL,6,FA woman from Somerset has told ITV
OL,7,FNews she cried after finding out that
OL,8,Fthe hospital she's due to give birth
OL,9,Fat within weeks is shutting part of
OL,10,Fits maternity service.
OL,12,FYeovil District Hospital is stopping
OL,13,Fbirths at its maternity unit from
OL,14,FMonday evening because of concerns
OL,15,Fover safety of care.
OL,17,FIn a statement the hospital trust said
OL,18,Fit 'cannot currently safely run the
OL,19,Funit' or 'safely provide care during
OL,20,Flabour and birth'.
