OL,3,CExpectant mum 'cried' when she found
OL,4,Cout maternity unit was closing
OL,6,FThe temporary closure comes after
OL,7,Fmaternity services at the hospital
OL,8,Fwere rated inadequate by the Care
OL,9,FQuality Commission (CQC), last year.
OL,11,FThe hospital was served a warning
OL,12,Fnotice "for failing to meet the
OL,13,Fregulations related to staffing and
OL,14,Fgovernance systems" following the CQC
OL,15,Finspection.
