OL,3,CExpectant mum 'cried' when she found
OL,4,Cout maternity unit was closing
OL,6,FOther maternity services, including
OL,7,Fantenatal appointments, are expected
OL,8,Fto continue at Yeovil during the six-
OL,9,Fmonth closure period.
OL,11,F'It's scary'
OL,13,FLocal mothers attending a local NCT
OL,14,Fclass shared their worries about the
OL,15,Ftemporary closure.
